attributes.action: Call a General election. We want Labour out.
attributes.additional_details:
Their decisions make no sense, they are driving business out of the country and cutting spending on the most vulnerable ie the disabled and elderly. 

How come you can only earn £404 pound on universal credit? How is this getting people into work?
attributes.background: The people would like Labour to gracefully remove themselves from parliament.

rejection.details:
You may wish to sign the following petition, which calls for similar action:

Call a General Election
https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/700143
